						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab in front of the temple of Basavēs11vara.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragmentary record registers a grant in memory of a hero (name not clear). <hi rend="bold">Basava</hi> and <hi rend="bold">Kētamalla</hi> are stated to be holding the office of <hi rend="italic">Gāvuṁḍu.</hi> It was written by <hi rend="bold">Māḷapayya,</hi> who was the teacher of <hi rend="bold">Kētamalla.</hi> The characters are of about the <hi rend="bold">11th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
